HEADWORD: Flexural
<hw>Flex"u*ral</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Flexure</er>.]</ety> <def>Of, pertaining to, or resulting from,
flexure; of the nature of, or characterized by, flexure; <as>as,
<ex>flexural</ex> elasticity</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

